{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":1681,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ていうか……この城の生き物だけでも、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I mean... just the creatures in this castle alone,"},{"lineNumber":1682,"originalJapaneseLine":"　変なの増えすぎでしょ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"there are way too many weird ones, right...?\""},{"lineNumber":1683,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うん。みんな面白いね！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yeah. Everyone is interesting!\""},{"lineNumber":1684,"originalJapaneseLine":"「………………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"............\""},{"lineNumber":1685,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あー、なるほどなー。まあ、そーね」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, I see. Well, yeah.\""},{"lineNumber":1686,"originalJapaneseLine":"「？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"?\""},{"lineNumber":1687,"originalJapaneseLine":"「や。大物になるわあんた。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Nah. You're going to become a big deal."},{"lineNumber":1688,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ああいや、もうなってるかな」","translatedEnglishLine":"Ah no, maybe you already are.\""},{"lineNumber":1689,"originalJapaneseLine":"「？？？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"???\""},{"lineNumber":1690,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なんでもなーい。さあ次、どんとこい」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It's nothing. Now then, bring on the next one.\""},{"lineNumber":1691,"originalJapaneseLine":"「てやーーー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Take this!\""},{"lineNumber":1692,"originalJapaneseLine":"かきかきと、地面に棒きれで","translatedEnglishLine":"Scribbling with a stick on the ground,"},{"lineNumber":1693,"originalJapaneseLine":"なんだかふわふわした、丸っこい生き物が描かれる。","translatedEnglishLine":"a somewhat fluffy, round creature is drawn."},{"lineNumber":1694,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ん、んん……？　また難しいわね、今回は……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, hmm...? This one's difficult again, huh...?\""},{"lineNumber":1695,"originalJapaneseLine":"「えーっ！　今回はすごく上手く描けたよ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ehh! This time I drew it really well!"},{"lineNumber":1696,"originalJapaneseLine":"　もうそのまんま！」","translatedEnglishLine":"It's pretty much spot on!\""},

{"lineNumber":1697,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ええぇ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ehh...\""},{"lineNumber":1698,"originalJapaneseLine":"「昨日、城の中で見かけたの。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I saw it inside the castle yesterday."},{"lineNumber":1699,"originalJapaneseLine":"　この近くだと思ったんだけど」","translatedEnglishLine":"I thought it was near here.\""},{"lineNumber":1700,"originalJapaneseLine":"「この近くで、って……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Near here, you say...?\""},{"lineNumber":1701,"originalJapaneseLine":"ハイジは促されるようにして周辺を見回し……","translatedEnglishLine":"Heidi was prompted to look around the surroundings..."},{"lineNumber":1702,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"............?\""},{"lineNumber":1703,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おわっ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Whoa...\""},{"lineNumber":1704,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ひゃー！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yikes!?\""},{"lineNumber":1705,"originalJapaneseLine":"反射的にリセットを抱えて、","translatedEnglishLine":"Reflexively, she grabbed Reset,"},{"lineNumber":1706,"originalJapaneseLine":"茂みの中に隠れた。","translatedEnglishLine":"and hid in the bushes."},{"lineNumber":1707,"originalJapaneseLine":"遠く、ほとんど視力の届かない間合いで、","translatedEnglishLine":"At a distance barely within sight range,"},{"lineNumber":1708,"originalJapaneseLine":"ビスケッタらしき影が、ハイジを見ていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"a silhouette resembling Biscetta was watching Heidi."},{"lineNumber":1709,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しまった、やばい……追っ手だ……！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Damn, this is bad... it's a pursuer...!"},{"lineNumber":1710,"originalJapaneseLine":"　見られた、メイド長……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"I've been spotted, the head maid...!\""},{"lineNumber":1711,"originalJapaneseLine":"「え、え、大丈夫？　叱られちゃう？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Eh, eh, are you okay? Are you going to get scolded?\""},{"lineNumber":1712,"originalJapaneseLine":"「んー、あー、それで済めばいいけど……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, ah, I hope it ends just with that...\""},{"lineNumber":1713,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………私のせいだって言う。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...They say it's my fault."},{"lineNumber":1714,"originalJapaneseLine":"　私がお願いしたって」","translatedEnglishLine":"That I was the one who asked for it.\""},{"lineNumber":1715,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そんな……いや、流石にそんな事は……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No way... no, surely not something like that...\""},{"lineNumber":1716,"originalJapaneseLine":"「………………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"............\""},{"lineNumber":1717,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うーん、そんな事はさせられないと思ったけど","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, I thought I wouldn't be allowed to do such a thing,"},{"lineNumber":1718,"originalJapaneseLine":"　客観的に考えるとそれが一番かなー。","translatedEnglishLine":"but objectively, that seems the best option."},{"lineNumber":1719,"originalJapaneseLine":"　うん、パンを一緒に食べた共犯という事もあるし」","translatedEnglishLine":"Yeah, considering we also ate bread together as accomplices.\""},{"lineNumber":1720,"originalJapaneseLine":"「え、え、あのパン、食べちゃダメだったの！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Eh, eh, we weren’t supposed to eat that bread!?\""},{"lineNumber":1721,"originalJapaneseLine":"「こちらのほうで、何か……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Over here, something...\""},{"lineNumber":1722,"originalJapaneseLine":"「わ、わ、あ、ビスケッタさん……！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"W-w-wait, Biscetta-san...!"},{"lineNumber":1723,"originalJapaneseLine":"　来たよ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"She's coming!\""},{"lineNumber":1724,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ここはもう！　お嬢様に全てをお任せして……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Right now! Let's leave everything to the young lady...\""},

{"lineNumber":1725,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……………………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"............\""},{"lineNumber":1726,"originalJapaneseLine":"と、ハイジは撤退路を探って、","translatedEnglishLine":"Heidi searched for a retreat route,"},{"lineNumber":1727,"originalJapaneseLine":"窓越しに城の中へと視線を向けて……","translatedEnglishLine":"and gazed inside the castle through the window..."},{"lineNumber":1728,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………………………あっ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...................Ah!\""},{"lineNumber":1729,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ゴキブリだーーーーーーー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It's a cockroach!!!!!!\""},{"lineNumber":1730,"originalJapaneseLine":"「えっ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Eh!?\""},{"lineNumber":1731,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふははははは！　獲ったーーーーー！！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hahahahaha! I got it!!!\""},{"lineNumber":1732,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ああんっ！　ハイジ先輩っ！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Aah! Heidi-senpai!?\""},{"lineNumber":1733,"originalJapaneseLine":"「奪われたっ……金一封！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It was snatched away... a cash reward!\""},{"lineNumber":1734,"originalJapaneseLine":"はぐれゴキブリの捕り物の騒ぎで、","translatedEnglishLine":"With the commotion of catching the stray cockroach,"},{"lineNumber":1735,"originalJapaneseLine":"ハイジのサボりは綺麗にうやむやにされた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Heidi's slacking off was neatly covered up."},{"lineNumber":1736,"originalJapaneseLine":"「見事です。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Well done."},{"lineNumber":1737,"originalJapaneseLine":"　今月のゴキブリ狩りはあなたがMVPでしょう」","translatedEnglishLine":"You should be the MVP of this month's cockroach hunt.\""},{"lineNumber":1738,"originalJapaneseLine":"「へっへへ。ごっちゃんです」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hehehe. Thanks a lot.\""},{"lineNumber":1739,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しかし――――自主休憩は褒められません。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"However ——— self-imposed breaks cannot be praised."},{"lineNumber":1740,"originalJapaneseLine":"　こちらは給金に影響させておきますよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"We'll make sure it affects your pay.\""}]}

